00:59:52.520 --> 00:59:56.480
Shall we say the mantra for the fire, Mother?

00:59:57.360 --> 01:00:00.680
We have to say together Shri Agni Devata, who is the Devi...

01:00:00.880 --> 01:00:04.560
Be careful about it. Don’t be too near. Little far away.

01:00:04.800 --> 01:00:08.600
It’s moving in all the directions.

01:00:09.840 --> 01:00:10.960
Now say the mantra.

01:00:11.160 --> 01:00:12.840
Shri Agni Devata who is a Devi,

01:00:13.040 --> 01:00:16.360
the aspect of fire in Shri Mataji.

01:00:42.200 --> 01:00:46.800
Shri SwahaSwamini who is a principle of...

01:00:52.960 --> 01:00:55.480
SM: I don’t know. How? What is the...? SY: SwahaSwamini.

01:00:55.680 --> 01:01:00.840
Swa-ha. Swaha is the quality of the... of the fire

01:01:01.080 --> 01:01:01.080
which consumes everything. Swa-ha.

01:01:35.200 --> 01:01:39.440
Now, after every name that he takes

01:01:39.640 --> 01:01:42.480
you have to take the thing from your hand like this,

01:01:42.680 --> 01:01:47.720
and take it round to the right side and put it in the fire.

01:01:47.920 --> 01:01:52.360
But those who haven't got these things in the hand

01:01:52.560 --> 01:01:55.440
should take up just their hand like that,

01:01:55.640 --> 01:01:57.920
thinking that they have it in their hand,

01:01:58.160 --> 01:02:03.200
and moving it upward like that and put it in the fire.

01:02:16.320 --> 01:02:19.480
And you all should say "Swaha".

01:02:23.920 --> 01:02:28.760
Now, just a minute. After every name, after every name.

01:02:32.960 --> 01:02:36.520
SY: The 108 names of Shri Vishnu. Yes, Mother, it’s all right?

01:02:36.720 --> 01:02:40.920
SM: First the Devi. SY: First the Devi.

01:18:15.040 --> 01:18:18.880
Now we'll do the Vishnu Sahasranama, hundred and eight.

01:18:19.120 --> 01:18:23.480
Again you distribute the [nuclear], distribute it.

01:18:44.280 --> 01:18:45.920
What’s the time now?

01:18:46.120 --> 01:18:49.360
SY: The time? It’s 2o’clock.

01:18:52.560 --> 01:18:57.160
We have only to be at6.30 here to[entice] later on.

