01:19:24.240 --> 01:19:26.920
You bring the oil and all that and you can massage him.

01:19:27.200 --> 01:19:29.760
SY: Yes, all right. We’ll give him a treatment.

01:19:29.960 --> 01:19:33.120
No problem. I think we can manage.

01:19:43.720 --> 01:19:46.680
Some people can go there and give them a practical session Mother.

01:19:46.880 --> 01:19:50.840
how to meditate in Sahaja Yoga, how to work on themselves...

01:19:51.040 --> 01:19:53.440
SM: So I said, 21 names of Vishnu are sufficient..

01:19:53.640 --> 01:19:56.120
SY: It’s all right, Mother. O.k.

